data.description: Clean and ready for immediate move in! This home has everything you have been looking for. Two living and dining areas. Family room has a built in desk and corner brick, floor to ceiling fireplace for those cool Texas evenings. The kitchen has a cooktop and built in oven and an abundance of cabinet and counter space. The breakfast bar is a perfect conversation area. Relax with a cool drink on the covered patio that over looks shady back yard. You will love this inviting neighborhood. Easy access to Loop 410, I-10, and 281. Shopping, restaurants, and entertainment close by.
